# airbyte_source_spacex_api (Resource)

SourceSpacexAPI Resource

## Example Usage

```terraform

  configuration = {
    id      = "5c9f06b5-482c-49eb-b700-3d0337f10a64"
    options = "...my_options..."
  }
  definition_id = "369e4ee3-2ccb-44d5-ada6-128f2436a122"
  name          = "Travis McCullough"
  secret_id     = "...my_secret_id..."

}
```
